`Tracking-Logik` `initialize` now sets `__trackingSessionEpoch` to the same `Date.now()` tick as the silence window and clears `devices` / `lastGoodPositionByDevice` / `lastPosition` first, so the map’s device list stays empty until a post-deploy MQTT point is accepted (UI “Verbunden” still follows `receivedAt` freshness in `Maplogik`).

